Class Enquiry

Object
Enquiry
All Implemented Interfaces:
IBaseSubmittableDocument, IReplyableDocument
public class Enquiry extends Object implements IReplyableDocument
This class represents an enquiry document submmited by a user regarding a specific BTO project.
